{
  "texts": [
    "Specifically, we applied thematic analysis using Tlab-10, a computerassisted qualitative analysis software, to unveil patterns, correlations, and recurring themes of information discussed on Quora, an online forum by Quora Inc., founded in 2009, allowing users to publish questions and answers on specific topics.",
    "Questions and answers are grouped by topic, allowing users to vote or comment.",
    "Additionally, users can collaborate by modifying questions or answers provided by others.",
    "We opted for this platform due to its public nature and unrestricted access to media content.",
    "Like social platforms such as Twitter, it offers the advantage of not imposing character limits."
  ]
}